summary:
Do you have a ton of stolen things and you don't like the the Ratway....
This mod adds Darnell Nugget into Whiterun to buy your questionable items...
descriptionHtml:
This mod Adds a Fence merchant to Whiterun located behind Adranas Forge. He sells some odd things But he will buy whatever you got wherever you got it.

He can also be your follower, so you can sell stolen things to him on the go.
PLEASE ENDORSE

CHECK OUT MY FOLLOWER COLLECTION BBFC

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50206/?
author: Darnell Nugget
